      "name": "Early Bird XOR Loader DLL",
      "description": "Custom x64 DLL (jopfgl.dll) compiled with GCC 15.1.0 MinGW. Exports: get_payload, inject_early_bird, xor_decrypt. Decrypts magde.dat with 32-byte XOR key and injects via Early Bird APC injection.",
